    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled right out of the showroom! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life and looks practically brand new inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s truly pristine and ready for the road, this is the one. Come take a look\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
