    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom-ready condition. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to be found, having been protected by a ceramic coating and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are firm and unmarked, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car has been pampered, maintained strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule with a complete folder of service records included. It drives as smoothly as the day it rolled off the assembly line, offering a tight, responsive experience with a whisper-quiet engine and seamless gear transitions. This is a rare, collector-quality example for the buyer who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
